FBIS3-16683 "drsov053_b_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Endorses Stepashin as Security Council Member LD1803091794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0848 GMT 18 Mar 94 LD1803091794 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow, 18 Mar -- President Boris Yeltsin today endorsed by decree Sergey Stepashin, director of the Federal Counter-Intelligence Service, as a member of the Russian Security Council. ITAR-TASS was informed of this today by the Russian president's press-service.
